bower info jquery   // get jquery versions for me
bower install jquery -g   // global
bower uninstall jquery
bower install bootstrap // updating a package

bower list
bower search angular ( get all packages have name angular )
make a folder for bower packages
    {
      "directory":"/bowering/data/welcome"
    }

saving that new package have been added bower.json file
    bower install underscore --save

getting cached packages in bower
    bower cache list

Installing package from cache
    bower install lodash -o

Installing package in a directorey
    bower install directory=lodash

getting package url in github
    bower lookup angular

publishing a package
    git init
    touch README.me
    touch .gitignore
    git add -A
    git commit -m "message"
    git remote add origin https://github.com/ahmeali/Singleton.git

make a release 0.0.1
    git tag 0.0.1
    git push --tags

making a bower register
    bower register package_name git:url